OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778234503
OL,3,CWoman who lost mum to MND gifts
OL,4,Cmystery parcels to raise awareness
OL,6,FA blind woman who lost her mum to
OL,7,Fmotor neurone disease (MND) is leaving
OL,8,Fmystery packages across Cardiff to
OL,9,Fspread awareness of the condition.
OL,11,FLaura Briars lost her mum Susan to the
OL,12,Fdisease eight years ago. They both
OL,13,Fshared a love of reading and now in
OL,14,Fher memory Laura makes parcels
OL,15,Fcontaining a book, some sweets and a
OL,16,FQR code to educate people about the
OL,17,Fillness and encourage donations.
OL,19,FLaura said her project, Parcels of
OL,20,FKindness, was inspired through this
OL,21,Fjoint passion.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778234503
OL,3,CWoman who lost mum to MND gifts
OL,4,Cmystery parcels to raise awareness
OL,6,F"Me and mum both found comfort in
OL,7,Fbooks. We both had different genres
OL,8,Fthat we leant towards...it's just
OL,9,Fsomething that was always close to our
OL,10,Fhearts."
OL,12,FAlongside her guide dog Greta, Laura
OL,13,Fthen travels to different places
OL,14,Facross Cardiff and leaves the packages
OL,15,Ffor people to find.
OL,17,FLaura explained that she hopes the
OL,18,Fparcels bring joy to the strangers who
OL,19,Ffind them.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778234503
OL,3,CWoman who lost mum to MND gifts
OL,4,Cmystery parcels to raise awareness
OL,6,F"I just hope it makes someone smile
OL,7,Fand makes them think that small acts
OL,8,Fof kindness can change a whole day of
OL,9,Fsomebody's life," she said.
OL,11,FRebecca Villard is a volunteer at the
OL,12,FMND Cardiff and Vale branch. She said
OL,13,FLaura's actions are vital in educating
OL,14,Fpeople about the condition.
OL,16,FShe explained: "It is a lovely thing
OL,17,FLaura is doing. It's a horrible
OL,18,Fdisease and it's crucial that we raise
OL,19,Fawareness to fund more research in
OL,20,Forder to keep helping those in our
OL,21,Fcommunity living with the disease.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,464,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778234503
OL,3,CWoman who lost mum to MND gifts
OL,4,Cmystery parcels to raise awareness
OL,6,F"In the Cardiff and Vale area we
OL,7,Fcurrently have 40 people living with
OL,8,Fthe disease, but of course there are
OL,9,Fmore than 40 people affected because
OL,10,Fall their family and friends will be
OL,11,Faffected by someone who has this awful
OL,12,Fdiagnosis."
OL,14,FMND is a progressive neurological
OL,15,Fcondition that affects nerves in the
OL,16,Fbrain and spinal cord. It causes
OL,17,Fmuscle weakening in the body, which
OL,18,Fcan impact a person's ability to walk
OL,19,Fand speak.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
