PN,46305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F463A1778234503
OL,3,CWoman who lost mum to MND gifts
OL,4,Cmystery parcels to raise awareness
OL,6,FAccording to Motor Neurone Disease
OL,7,FAssociation, more than 250 people in
OL,8,FWales live with the condition.
OL,10,FThe QR code in Laura's book parcels
OL,11,Flead to a JustGiving page, fundraising
OL,12,Ffor Motor Neurone Disease Association.
OL,14,FShe has raised more than #200 for the
OL,15,Fcharity through the mystery parcels.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
